   <h1 class="text-center">
    Welcome to the Belfast Girl Gang Website!
   </h1>
   <br>
   <p class="text-center"> 
   
    The aim of the Belfast Girl Gang is to bring gals together from across Northern Ireland to make memories, form friendships, and make life a lil' less lonely. <br>
<br>
    With over 2100 of us, the Belfast Girl Gang community has your back. 
   
<br>
<br>
We want this to be a place where everyone can feel comfortable, happy, safe, and at home. This includes welcoming and inclusive to all who identify as a woman or non-binary. 

<br>
<br>
This is a safe space, so have fun here, this is OUR community. 
</p>
